{"tid":2197591,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix睇返哥普拉套吸血殭屍驚情400年","createTime":"2020-09-10T17:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T16:12:42.000Z","uid":134683,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c61488a9faa5922c23cc5a18c7db5bde04024fb1","tid":2197591,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mouyBrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmouyBrx.jpg&h=453368b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識欣賞冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先一口氣煲完成成套<br />\n美術指導同服裝都係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個鏡頭運用同燈光好考究<br />\n劇情就無謂講太耳熟能詳<br />\n純睇故事嘅一定會嗌救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但故事佈局同氣氛好有古典小說色彩<br />\n導演對文學嘅消化能力真係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外選角又係無敵<br />\n加利奧文當年已經爐火純青<br />\n淨係睇佢個人表現已經係一種享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NKOqm0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NKOqm0.jpg&h=1127a9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外奇洛李維斯同雲露娜維達<br />\n兩個當年好pure好true<br />\n兩個都靚到好似童話世界走出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揀佢兩個拍古典小說真係一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYQxR2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYQxR2F.jpg&h=b0036200&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGjVPPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGjVPPm.jpg&h=7fdeabaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qa6b2J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qa6b2J.gif&h=ee789721&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHsPUf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHsPUf3.jpg&h=8c9044aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個最近合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w21tqn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw21tqn5.jpg&h=3c4947aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec69da95b7a1c0db31f71561d9feb0b60a633a0","tid":2197591,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f10cb7ee4639de993895ef47d4f9dc5e5202c90","tid":2197591,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">以前</span>完全唔識欣賞冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141c89593b89dc81d8e784bea4a60cdcc8876471","tid":2197591,"uid":25653,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"will?will~~~~"},{"pid":"3ada7729b4ef80f12a126a240c47865fd601ddcd","tid":2197591,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"是的好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9718dcc9ebec618beea237991090867e9a010","tid":2197591,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733c6db8f77509379940d557ac5253b7ccec7161","tid":2197591,"uid":129660,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:00:24.000Z","msg":"正評是給乳搖的"},{"pid":"ce8e55cc705741d40cdafca268b4c9340c137890","tid":2197591,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"733c6db8f77509379940d557ac5253b7ccec7161","tid":2197591,"uid":129660,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:00:24.000Z","msg":"正評是給乳搖的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"多謝哥普拉<i